{"word":"κουρίζω","slug":"κουρίζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>κουρίζω</b></el> <el>(κουρίζω,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><el>κόρος, κοῦρος</el>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><a href='S:intransitive'>intr.</a> <i>to be a youth</i>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:transitive'>trans.</a> <i>to bring up from boyhood</i>, <b><a href='S:Hesiod'>Hes.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}